    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Recently, I just started to read a book called "The road less travelled". It introduce four disciplines:</p>

<pre><code>Delay satisfaction 延迟满足
Take responsibilites 承担责任
Seek truth 献身真理
Keep balance 保持平衡
</code></pre>

<p>Life is suffering. Disciplines make life less suffering.</p>
